The Problem: Given a massive server log file, extract only the lines that contain the word "ERROR".
The Secret: This is often a "Map-Only" job. You don't actually need a Reducer to aggregate anything; you just need the Mapper to filter out the noise.

Mapper Key: The entire log line.

Mapper Value: None (or empty).

